          </div>

          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-header">
              <span class="faq-question-text">How can I be considered for Early Access?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-accordion-content">
              <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                <p>You may kindly submit your interest by registering your email or contacting us directly. Our staff would be happy to assist.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-header">
              <span class="faq-question-text">How will I know if I’ve been selected?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-accordion-content">
              <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                <p>Selected individuals will be notified directly via email.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Shipping & Delivery -->
      <div class="faq-section-group">
        <h2 class="faq-section-title">3. Shipping & Delivery</h2>
        <div class="faq-accordions">

          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-header">
              <span class="faq-question-text">What is the delivery timeline?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-accordion-content">
              <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                <p>Ready-to-ship orders are delivered within 3–7 business days.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-header">
              <span class="faq-question-text">How can I track my order?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-accordion-content">
              <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                <p>A tracking link is shared upon dispatch. You will also receive order updates via email.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-accordion-item">
            <div class="faq-accordion-header">
